HALLWAY OF HEADSHOTS! Building a community here has been a great blessing. I’ve found where I belong in this moment, in this chapter of my life. I now realize why I LOVE Halloween so much, it allowed me the opportunity to do what I love most. ACT. Becoming something other than myself and fully committing to that. It’s not about the ghouls and monsters but a reminder of the challenge it would be to portray something so opposite of myself. I get to play. In that I am most happiest. It’s the scariest most fulfilling thing I’ve ever done. That is what calls to me most in this life and that is what I shall chase for the rest of it. HAPPY HALLOWEEN EVE KIDDOS🎃 may we all remember to play!!
